s sidebar expand with a click, and a hover-revealed `View project` button opens the project page",id:"Adm40w2OOS"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"When a remote session's working folder has been deleted, `Fork session` recovers it into a fresh worktree",id:"FKMFf4iqY+"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"The floating side chat ([[cmd+;]]) remembers where you placed and sized it",id:"yxzcnV4kDy"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"[[cmd+k]] finds sessions you started since opening the app, and searches branches inside folders",id:"os5Efgh+1R"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`Add plugin` from the + menu opens straight to the installable plugin list",id:"BWNg2tVBBL"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Rename from the sidebar's right-click menu edits the name in place",id:"XRbDTrjI0c"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Sessions with an open draft PR no longer show or sort as closed",id:"J8WyagGCb5"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Dropdowns near the top of the window are clickable instead of dragging the window",id:"FsajkwOAiZ"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"SSH session setup works when the remote home directory is on a network filesystem",id:"huzigEoZJv"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Tables in popout windows use the right font size",id:"ITKXJOdd9C"})}]},{version:"1.10628.0",date:"2026-06-02",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Choose effort with a slider next to the model picker",id:"uYLQ5lDLZu"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Mark a waiting session as completed from the sidebar's right-click menu \u2014 clears the yellow dot without sending a reply",id:"4HrerxXUg5"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"When the model is overloaded, pick a different one right from the error card's retry menu",id:"giU3LRQe8Q"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"The Files panel stays open when you switch between sessions",id:"Jdr9gPxUIc"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Usage-limit notices now say which limit you hit and when it resets",id:"0bIJknc5LK"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Press a number key to pick an option when Claude asks a question",id:"icn8CM+0cV"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Opening a very large repository no longer crashes on startup",id:"Vqd9xnOl2k"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"The diff panel and file previews work in SSH sessions",id:"gC9+SjQopv"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Sessions in their own window stay responsive when the main window is hidden",id:"VHhN1KfmCH"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Archiving or deleting a session works while it's starting up or responding",id:"hEM4asyIjl"})}]},{version:"1.9659.0",date:"2026-05-28",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Claude Opus 4.8 is now available in the model picker",id:"BBdIiDX7hr"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Dynamic workflows let Claude fan out to many subagents on a single task",id:"8By5nlWG7I"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Your `WorktreeCreate` and `WorktreeRemove` hooks run for local sessions too \u2014 jj and Sapling setups can use worktree isolation",id:"de6C2Wzbse"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Searching file contents with `?` works for folders that aren't git repos",id:"CjsWsZhIqS"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Agents you define in your project's `.claude/agents` show up in the `@`-mention picker \u2014 and new ones appear without a restart",id:"JjAk5QHGza"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"The PR bar finds your open PR even when your local branch name doesn't match the remote's",id:"dN1nhuij65"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Local video attachments play in the lightbox",id:"6p+YJwQX1o"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Starting a session on a branch works with macOS's built-in git",id:"VZeCi0uoZQ"})}]},{version:"1.9255.0",date:"2026-05-26",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Split view now tiles into an adaptive grid \u2014 fit more sessions on a wide screen",id:"8vlKwS/pfy"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`/rename` renames the current session",id:"1iTX3zl2VF"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`/compact` now shows a marker in the transcript where context was compacted",id:"DAJYQ+55MZ"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Get a desktop notification when a routine run fails",id:"EHpObemtru"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Remote Control shows as a badge in the title bar \u2014 click it to turn on or off",id:"M5bEHfdTTK"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Click an image path in a response to preview it, even when it's outside your project folder",id:"iKUOEsCesf"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Files you reference with `@` show as chips in the transcript, not just videos",id:"yNWdRZLhMh"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Queued messages collapse into a stack \u2014 click to expand",id:"CCGNwmhrOs"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Bash commands in the transcript are syntax-highlighted",id:"SzTj8drdXm"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Your most recent sessions open faster from the sidebar",id:"XjwwQZQC/4"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Trackpad scrolling works over code and diff blocks",id:"kVrDy/v1HF"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"The transcript stays where you scrolled instead of snapping back to the bottom",id:"rxO0yeSTDT"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Cancelling a queued message no longer interrupts the turn in progress",id:"P63xgHSKex"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Sessions with uncommitted changes are no longer auto-archived",id:"pNZUCYa4jA"})}]},{version:"1.8555.1",date:"2026-05-22",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Open a session in its own window to work on sessions side by side \u2014 drag it out from the sidebar, or [[cmd+click]] it",id:"ZGvkX6TY8M"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Auto mode is now available on the Pro plan \u2014 Sonnet 4.6 is now supported, alongside Opus 4.7",id:"QnA8VUIvVj"})}]},{version:"1.8555.0",date:"2026-05-21",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Videos you attach appear as chips in the transcript \u2014 click to play",id:"iRvW/9oStG"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Click a `#L5-L20` link in a response to highlight those lines in the file panel",id:"jPM3XrqpC3"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`file://` paths in responses are now clickable",id:"fCqsyH2TG3"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Remote sessions reconnect on their own after sleep or network changes",id:"ZWsDyQeFPt"})}]},{version:"1.8089.0",date:"2026-05-19",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Group sessions by PR state from the filter icon at the top of the sidebar",id:"X707sOR++o"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"[[cmd+u]] attaches a file from your computer",id:"qUTTUrFL4F"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Sessions remember your scroll position when you come back to them",id:"jfGIZALMiO"})}]},{version:"1.7196.0",date:"2026-05-15",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Pick your code font and theme in `Settings \u2192 Claude Code \u2192 Appearance`",id:"R4cKoaRG3c"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Get a desktop notification when Claude finishes while you're in another app",id:"EJgFVunmTS"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"[[ctrl+]]] and [[ctrl+[]] cycle focus between split panes",id:"1pDTicCdea"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Move a local session to the cloud from its `\u2022\u2022\u2022` menu so it keeps running when you close your laptop",id:"2Mt/gDql/P"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`/usage` shows your token usage for the current session inline",id:"MJeNpHWSBI"})},{kind:"fix",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Dotfiles show up in the file tree and `@`-mention search",id:"ZloNHabIoM"})}]},{version:"1.6608.0",date:"2026-05-07",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Create and name your own session groups \u2014 drag sessions in, or right-click a session \u2192 `Move to group`",id:"NAen74+5KK"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Click any file in the file panel to edit it in place",id:"fKFZn3x9/k"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Turn on Remote Control for all new local sessions in `Settings \u2192 Claude Code`",id:"BWYONtbtL0"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Resolved review comments collapse in the diff view so you can focus on what's open",id:"g8jaGMlx3n"})}]},{version:"1.6259.0",date:"2026-05-05",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Attach up to 20 images in a single message for local sessions",id:"AtQI4gQ2Qm"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:'"Always allow" choices now persist after you quit the app',id:"tQkGeo/pLH"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Sidebar pins and starred sessions survive sign-out",id:"+qm9S5DZcB"})}]},{version:"1.5354.0",date:"2026-04-29",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`/btw` or [[cmd+;]] opens a side chat with Claude without interrupting your main session",id:"oCUtTGiVOc"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Open multiple terminal tabs in the terminal pane",id:"KpxLln6Tcc"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Right-click any folder in the file tree \u2192 `Open in terminal`",id:"o93iHAIei0"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Queue follow-up messages while Claude is still working \u2014 they send automatically when it's ready",id:"FJeVTW7t3g"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"See related and stacked PRs together in the PR bar",id:"nzAlf/Dr9C"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Sort sessions from the filter icon in the sidebar",id:"bfrtsSnP8t"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`/feedback` sends feedback about the current session without leaving it",id:"vMDozLqrrm"})}]},{version:"1.4758.0",date:"2026-04-24",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Drag, resize, and keyboard-navigate split panes with sessions side by side",id:"JR1Xo64s7i"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Draw directly on the preview to show Claude what you mean \u2014 click the pencil icon in the preview toolbar",id:"VN6sKZ3xLJ"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Markdown files render as formatted previews in the file panel",id:"Gls6MqqVlD"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Right-click any file in the diff tree for `Open`, `Copy path`, and `Attach as context`",id:"s1HEb7obG9"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Archive or delete several sessions at once from the Recents header menu",id:"oWtfUA9kKn"})}]},{version:"1.3883.0",date:"2026-04-21",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`Open in editor` from the diff view or a session's right-click menu",id:"eAyw5h1GYi"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Right-click any image in a response to `Copy` or `Save` it",id:"Ka5fuL2X+i"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`#123` and bare URLs in your messages become clickable links",id:"EBLto6Usbn"})}]},{version:"1.3561.0",date:"2026-04-20",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Browse your project's files in a side pane \u2014 fuzzy-find by name, search contents with `?`, [[cmd+f]] to find in file",id:"h9861zcdct"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"`/model` switches the model mid-session",id:"Awv67vzgyK"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Right-click any message \u2192 `Copy as Markdown` or `Copy link`",id:"XZBHNaDiVC"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Every folder you've worked in appears under Recent \u2014 click the `+` next to one to start a session there",id:"66GrxvW+G9"})},{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Right-click a message or select text \u2192 `Attach as context` to reference it in your next message",id:"I6tIchIFGY"})},{kind:"improvement",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Math renders inline in responses",id:"N/ByQVfDc5"})}]},{version:"1.3109.0",date:"2026-04-16",items:[{kind:"feat",text:nT({defaultMessage:"Toggle Fast mode f